00:22:58,590 --> 00:22:59,310
Stop!

290
00:23:12,980 --> 00:23:13,780
Stop running!

291
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:14,440
Stop!

292
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:39,910
Why are they only chasing me?

293
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:48,980
A flare shot.

294
00:23:53,130 --> 00:23:56,480
[Priest Su Ya's Mansion]

295
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,420
Shrimpie,

296
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:06,210
what happened to you?

297
00:26:10,540 --> 00:26:12,200
Someone, go check over there!

298
00:27:11,780 --> 00:27:13,180
Shrimpie, where are you?

299
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:36,090
They just ran this way. Search.

300
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:37,640
See where they all are.

301
00:28:04,810 --> 00:28:06,140
Open all these coffins.

302
00:28:10,540 --> 00:28:11,070
Nothing.

303
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,360
Nothing.

304
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:32,830
Shh.

305
00:29:38,330 --> 00:29:39,390
We are safe for now.

306
00:29:39,850 --> 00:29:40,330
You...

307
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,780
Are you crazy? What's wrong with you?

308
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:42,500
I... you...

309
00:29:42,530 --> 00:29:43,490
I think there's something wrong with you.

310
00:29:43,490 --> 00:29:44,190
Robber!

311
00:29:44,220 --> 00:29:44,630
Hooligan!

312
00:29:44,630 --> 00:29:45,430
Stop arguing.

313
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:47,160
You two gave me a headache.

314
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:51,070
Why did you take someone's thigh bone?

315
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,110
Send it back.

316
00:29:53,810 --> 00:29:55,540
I know how to find Zhang Qiling.

317
00:29:57,420 --> 00:29:58,570
Who is Zhang Qiling?

318
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,530
None of your business.

319
00:30:00,980 --> 00:30:02,680
She is my sister.

320
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:03,950
Who do you think you are?

321
00:30:03,950 --> 00:30:05,010
She is my mentor's wife.

322
00:30:05,010 --> 00:30:07,070
Stop claiming false relationships.

323
00:30:17,220 --> 00:30:18,680
The marks on this bone

324
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:21,200
were left by the Zhang family's
unique bone-scraping tool.

325
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,480
If I'm not mistaken,

326
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:24,570
the chief must have handled these bones.

327
00:30:24,570 --> 00:30:26,090
So as long as we figure out

328
00:30:26,090 --> 00:30:27,590
where these bones came from,

329
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:28,550
we can find him.

330
00:30:29,090 --> 00:30:29,940
Little Taoist,

331
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,830
do you know any place in Bailejing

332
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:33,890
that specializes in handling bones?

333
00:30:35,380 --> 00:30:36,580
I actually do.

334
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:40,930
Xigudong, one of the Six Great Fortresses
of Nanqiang.

335
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:43,150
The people in Bailejing believe

336
00:30:43,150 --> 00:30:45,610
that a person's skin, flesh, and bones

337
00:30:45,630 --> 00:30:47,220
are 3 different things.

338
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:48,660
Flesh has the shortest lifespan,

339
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:50,980
so people can only live
as long as their flesh lives.

340
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:52,460
But bones are different.

341
00:30:53,060 --> 00:30:54,920
Bones have the longest lifespan.

342
00:30:55,050 --> 00:30:57,590
Forty-nine days after death,
the skin dies.

343
00:30:57,610 --> 00:30:59,330
And 30 years after death,

344
00:30:59,450 --> 00:31:00,730
the bones finally die.

345
00:31:00,750 --> 00:31:01,530
So they believe

346
00:31:01,530 --> 00:31:03,350
that physical death is not true death.

347
00:31:03,350 --> 00:31:05,850
As for the bones
stripped of skin and flesh,

348
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:08,110
they are sent to Xigudong to be washed

349
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,440
and then returned to their relatives.

350
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,330
Xigudong?

351
00:31:11,580 --> 00:31:12,770
Where is the entrance?

352
00:31:12,770 --> 00:31:13,830
Do you know the way?

353
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:17,870
I don't know.

354
00:31:18,290 --> 00:31:20,080
I thought you knew everything.

355
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:20,890
But I know,

356
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:22,780
among the Six Great Fortresses
of Nanqiang,

357
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:24,030
only the outermost Bailejing

358
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:24,900
allows outsiders to enter.

359
00:31:24,900 --> 00:31:25,940
The rest do not.

360
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,080
Moreover,

361
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,790
among these fortresses,

362
00:31:28,790 --> 00:31:30,320
there is an unwritten rule.

363
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:31,660
That is, in each fortress,

364
00:31:31,660 --> 00:31:32,770
only a very few people

365
00:31:32,770 --> 00:31:34,670
know how to enter the next fortress.

366
00:31:34,670 --> 00:31:36,600
The mountain roads and valleys
are complicated,

367
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,660
just like a maze.

368
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:39,830
I don't think we can get in.

369
00:31:41,810 --> 00:31:43,660
Are you going to Xigudong to find someone?

370
00:31:43,660 --> 00:31:44,570
I heard that Bailejing

371
00:31:44,570 --> 00:31:46,140
holds a Bone-Washing Ceremony every year,

372
00:31:46,140 --> 00:31:47,450
and it's happening in these two days.

373
00:31:47,450 --> 00:31:49,300
You can participate
as long as you prepare a set of bones.

374
00:31:49,300 --> 00:31:49,950
But...

375
00:31:50,290 --> 00:31:51,050
for the Bone-Washing Ceremony,

376
00:31:51,050 --> 00:31:53,350
the bones need to be at least
10 years old.

377
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:02,260
How many years has your mentor been dead?

378
00:32:05,490 --> 00:32:10,070
[Mentor Zhang Qianzhang's Tomb]

379
00:32:10,300 --> 00:32:12,740
Mentor, I'm sorry.

380
00:32:17,550 --> 00:32:19,090
Mentor,

381
00:32:19,090 --> 00:32:20,950
I am so sorry.

382
00:32:21,660 --> 00:32:23,740
I am sorry.

383
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,310
I didn't want this either.

384
00:32:28,940 --> 00:32:30,290
That's enough.

385
00:32:47,570 --> 00:32:48,350
Don't you...

386
00:32:49,570 --> 00:32:51,160
have anything to say to him?

387
00:33:11,670 --> 00:33:13,150
Then stay one more night.

388
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:15,640
We must go to Xigudong tomorrow.

389
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:19,780
Also,

390
00:33:19,860 --> 00:33:21,190
call Zhang Hailou back.

391
00:34:08,170 --> 00:34:09,159
A flare shot.

